{
  "stem": "16245.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then later, the Spain-- the Spanish Civil War would have been a catalyst to political consciousness as the Vietnam War would have been to a lot of Australian kids.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I don't remember them obviously, just the flavor of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Naturally, Jews couldn't be in-- in favor of Hitler and company.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Look, there-- there were Zionists around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Jewish kids who were in Zionist organizations-- and obviously, there were Zionist organizations-- it was discouraged by our parents, our teachers, our rabbis.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was in bad [? order. ?]",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was really quite ignorant about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, as a little kid, I was really quite ignorant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know what it was about.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, obviously, we were citizens of Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of-- to be sure, of Jewish persuasion, but we were brought up to be patriotic Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it simply didn't make sense to pick yourself up and go to-- to the Middle East.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was a private school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And put it in the Melbourne context, well, let's say Melbourne grammar-- Scotch, if you like.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but that was 1936, 1937.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by then, anti-Semitism was-- was really-- there, it was quite unbearable.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the teachers unfailingly picked on you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were some who were sympathetic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The headmaster, for instance, was a reasonable man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But one or two teachers were absolutely rabid anti-Semites.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the children in my class were not too bad, because they put all the Jews in the one class together with all the Protestants.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that there were four or five parallel classes that were 100% Catholic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then there was one class half Jewish, half Protestant, and a sprinkling of Catholics to make up the numbers.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
